name: Online_Shopping_App_monolothic
description: This is a practical example of NodeJS Microservices Architecture. We have built a simple Online Grocery Shopping Application using ES6 in a Monolithic way and segregate in Microservices Architecture without impact frontend. So each individual service will work independently to serve the purpose and business logic.
